prints.expr:
let rawName = "   alice  " in
  let radius = 3.0 in
  let name = String.uppercase_ascii (String.trim (rawName)) in
  let area = (3.141592653589793 *. Float.pow (radius) (2.0)) in
  print_endline (String.concat " " ["Hello"; (name ^ "!")]);
  print_endline (String.concat " " ["The area of a circle with radius"; Printf.sprintf "%.15f" (radius); "is"; Printf.sprintf "%.15f" (area)])
